_sText:
This is my first full map, so I'm ready for some feedback.

There are three paths to take: The door, the vent, and the roof. All three sort of lead back to the main rooms so it's a small fast map.

Let me know what you think!

Thanks,
Backslash

P.S. If you decide to use this on your server, post a link to it in the comments section so people can see it in action.
